entries.quest_destroy_d: In an effort to cripple the Binayre Pirates, destroy five of their Black Jacks.
entries.quest_location_d: The Binayre Pirates tend to hunt in the Corellia system.  Go there to hunt them down.
entries.title: Corellia System: Seek and Destroy 5 Binayre ships.
entries.title_d: Travel to the Corellia system, hunt down, and destroy five Binayre Black Jacks. You will receive navigational points of common Binayre activity. When you complete this mission, return to Ceth Laike at the Imperial Outpost on Talus.
